commit.message:
Make-lang.in, [...]: Update copyright.

	* Make-lang.in, call.c, class.c, decl2.c, except.c, expr.c,
	init.c, mangle.c, typeck.c: Update copyright.

From-SVN: r76304

files.patch:

+2004-01-21  Kazu Hirata  <kazu@cs.umass.edu>
+
+	* Make-lang.in, call.c, class.c, decl2.c, except.c, expr.c,
+	init.c, mangle.c, typeck.c: Update copyright.
+
